      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Clean, well-kept, and ready to enjoy, this is a good-condition example that offers strong overall appeal at a fair price. It presents nicely inside and out, with the kind of cared-for feel that makes it easy to appreciate, while still showing the light signs of use you\u2019d expect from an honest driver. A great choice for someone looking for a sharp, solid car without paying mint-condition money.",
