      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable, affordable, and priced to move, this vehicle is a smart option for buyers who want straightforward transportation without stretching the budget. It shows its age, but it still offers solid day-to-day usefulness and an excellent opportunity for a value-focused driver, first-time buyer, or anyone needing an inexpensive backup vehicle. An honest car at a practical price, ready for its next owner.",
