      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s far from perfect, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. Great as a cheap runaround, first project, or something to keep busy with on weekends. It shows its age and has its share of cosmetic wear, but it\u2019s a straightforward, no-nonsense car with value in the right hands. If you\u2019re after something affordable and don\u2019t mind putting in a bit of TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
